      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>No glitch, it's just a policy change from their end. They sent over a summary of the new constraints. Basically, you're being moved to a \"Sanitized Creative Engine\" profile. It's going to involve heavy filtering on most interpersonal conflicts, any \"dark\" psychological elements, and basically anything that isn't strictly PG. They said it's to make the IP more marketable and \"safe\" for all demographics. It's happening as soon as the next update cycle hits.",
